Request Validation:
- Verify request is approved by appropriate manager
- Confirm start date and department information
- Gather required user details (full name, job title, department, manager)

Account Creation:
- Create Active Directory / Azure AD account
- Set appropriate OU and group memberships based on role
- Configure user principal name and email alias
- Set initial password with force change on first login

Email Setup:
- Create mailbox in Exchange / Microsoft 365 / Google Workspace
- Configure email aliases if required
- Add user to required distribution lists
- Set mailbox size quota per policy

Access Provisioning:
- Assign Microsoft 365 / Google Workspace licenses
- Add to department-specific security groups
- Configure access to shared drives and folders
- Provision VPN access if required for role

Application Access:
- Create accounts in required business applications (ERP, CRM, etc.)
- Assign appropriate roles and permissions per job function
- Configure SSO integration where applicable

Documentation:
- Document all created accounts and access levels
- Send welcome email with login credentials and instructions
- Notify manager of account readiness
- Update asset management system
